      <title>俄罗斯反战候选人收集签名挑战普京</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/russian-anti-war-candidate-gathers-signatures-to-challenge-putin</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位致力于结束俄罗斯在乌克兰战争的政客已收集了超过 10 万个签名，以在 3 月份的总统选举中挑战弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin)。这并不意味着他会被允许参选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/russian-anti-war-candidate-gathers-signatures-to-challenge-putin</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 15:55:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
